})
export class AppModule { }
```

Please ensure that you provide the relative path correctly based on your folder structure and the location of the built microfrontend bundles.

If you still encounter the "cannot find module" error, double-check that the microfrontend projects are built successfully and their output files are accessible from the main project's folder structure.

